            <li><strong>For Legal Reasons:</strong> We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.</li>
            <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets, your information may be transferred.</li>
        </ul>

